#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Listen to free music published under Creative Common licenses. See also "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en/about\">Jamendo.com</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Escuche música libre publicada con licencia Creative Common. Consulte "
